Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H242B96&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Godradamus' Great Prophecy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,110, police? I need help!\NSomeone's chasing me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, girl. That's a testing chamber for GOD's Killer Smog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!! Let me out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulysses...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for orders from the Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come to cover Tokyo with\NKiller Smog in our Tokyo Annihilation Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulysses, you will coordinate the operation and\Nstop GOD's enemy, the X Rider, from interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood? You must contain the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A strategy to contain the X Rider, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll start by drawing him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulysses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of GOD's Secret Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that. The Secret Police will\Nbe cooperating fully in this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of luring the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Keisuke's friend, but...\NAny special reason you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be vague or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late! Your friend's been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look-- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A snobby guy, all dressed in white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apol-- That was him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Incantation){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist lost me in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This prophet's spouting some real nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Prophet?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He said Tokyo's going to be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have seen a vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust in Godradamus' words!\NTokyo will be annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The day... Today!\NThe time... 3pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At that hour, every human in Tokyo will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run! Abandon Tokyo\Nand run while you yet live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!\NHow can you justify this claim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Prophecy needs no justification!\NThe proof... is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, don't listen to this rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Uematsu, a geophysicist\Nat Touwa University.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Academically and scientifically, there's no\Nway Tokyo can just be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I see a non-believer,\Ndying in a most cruel fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Godradamus' prophecies are 99% accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, prophesies don't come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... No sign of the prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone's ringing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing. Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew GOD was behind this. What's the\Nmeaning of these weird prophesies!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's great prophecy is no lie.\NTokyo will perish at Ulysses' hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You think I'll\Nlet you get away with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can stop us, Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That telephone booth is one\Nof GOD's gas execution chambers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gas execution chambers!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His flesh and bones will have melted\Nby now. Deactivate the Killer Smog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! Jin Keisuke - no, the X Rider,\Nhas been reduced to nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he run away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulysses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't run anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you interfering!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself! This is not the\Ntime to fight with the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That strategy is over. Leave him to me,\Nand accelerate preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! I'll spare you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to tell me\Neverything about GOD's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you'll have to catch me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! No leads on GOD...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Maybe there's one lead left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Uematsu Geophysics Research Lab{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Death to the professor... Thus spake the\Ninflexible voice of God in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run! Abandon Tokyo\Nand run while you yet live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hiroko?\N-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The prophet! The prophet was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one else here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been daydreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth! He said you'd die, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you give me that silly look too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I don't believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't answer the phone, dad!\NThe prophet said you'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroko, you're a scientist's daughter.\NYou shouldn't believe in prophecies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get back to your homework, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Uematsu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Godradamus has prophesied that you will die cruelly and fall into Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! Do you think...\NDo you think I believe that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's great prophecy is no lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that prophet...\NHow did you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Many heard me prophesy your death.\NAs such, I must ensure it comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To create the World of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You rotten prophet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to discuss GOD's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I prophesied...\NTokyo will be wiped out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is GOD's plan!\NAnd I am its coordinator!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your true identity is Ulysses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well deciphered, Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever that nosy Apollo Geist\Nsays, I'll kill you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulysses Killer Smog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't last long at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I nearly had him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The family have fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! It's nearly time to\Nbegin the plan... Back to base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes until GOD's prophecy\Nof Tokyo's annihilation comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon my Killer Smog will spray from\Nevery telephone receiver in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a trace of its population will be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you to your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ulysses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To ensure GOD's prophecy comes true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must first kill these three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you caught them, Apollo Geist?\NVery well then, execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darling!\N-Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, at least spare them! The prophet\Nonly predicted my death! Right? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late! Circumstances have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist, how can you say that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimate GOD's Secret Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! I played along\Njust to be sure it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!? When did he--?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plan to annihilate Tokyo\Nthrough its phone lines is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! The countdown will start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can watch the end\Nof Tokyo from that pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're... they're really\Ngoing to annihilate Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting countdown. Minus twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nineteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Suction Magnets!\N-Fifteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's the Killer Smog?\N-Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry, but your Killer Smog's valve stays shut!\N-Seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Curse you, X Rider!\N-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's great prophecy must be realised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I already cut the connection between\Nthe phone lines and gas cans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you... X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulysses Crown Binding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like my head's splitting...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Electro Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll join the great Ulysses in death...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the end of Ulysses?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief of the Secret Police\Nhas a prophecy of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear on the name of\NApollo Geist... that I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:23:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist has personally\Nchallenged the X Rider at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How will the X Rider fight one so\Nterrifyingly intelligent and strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(0,7)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD revives the 'Mad Bugs,' extinct\Nfor 2,000 years, to drive Japan insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And a spectacular fight unfolds when\NKamen Rider X accepts Apollo Geist's challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end of Apollo Geist at last?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Apollo Geist's Mad Bug Hell"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider